Synopsis: The battle has been wearing Daisy down and the voice of the Absolute grows stronger the closer we are to it. Daisy is struggling, but wants to know how were doing, and complements us on our progress so far. Relationship-building and trust consolidation - brings us closer to the intimacy we need for romance in Act 3.
